'''Hannah Blessing Wood''' (born [[1983]]) is a poet, and also the sister of [[Elijah Wood]]. She appeared in minor roles without lines in two of her brother's movies, 
''[[wikipedia:Radio Flyer (film)|Radio Flyer]]'' and ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]'', where she played a girl sheltering in the [[Glittering Caves]].
